        368.4700012207031,
        130.388916015625
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "学检查证实，并须满足下列全部条件：",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        184.61000061035156,
        135.7889404296875,
        460.29998779296875,
        146.34893798828125
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "（1）总胆红素和直接胆红素同时升高，血清ALP>200U/L；",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        184.61000061035156,
        151.86895751953125,
        300.19000244140625,
        162.428955078125
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "（2）持续性黄疸病史；",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
        184.61000061035156,
        167.82891845703125,
        363.19000244140625,
        178.388916015625
      ],
      "max_font_size": 10.5600004196167,
      "text": "（3）出现胆汁性肝硬化或门脉高压。",
      "is_heading": false
    },
    {
      "bbox": [
